Linux and shell scripting:
OS:it will acts as a interface betweeen the software(user) and hardware(cpu,ram,i/o).
-->LINUX VS WINDOWS
-->Os contains kernal(Heart of os),sys lib,compilers,user processers,system softwares
     ->Kernal is mainly responsiable for thr four things
         =>Device management
         =>Memory management
         =>process management
         =>System calls

    ->sys lib are mainly responsiable for the performing the task given by the user

Shell scripting:
->In linux we are talking with the os by shell commands
->The list of shell commands is called shell scripting
